{"tid":220776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦王振民：即使回歸時有內戰，也是要回歸祖國","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T15:09:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d33b5f8c5c3ad9a4619bf500a4620a3b6e4665eb","tid":220776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"中聯辦法律部部長王振民出席《紫荊》一國兩制論壇致辭時，指由1985至1990年制訂《基本法》、到1997香港回歸時，中國不是一張白紙，不是沒有憲法、沒有制度的國家，而且香港這「遊子」離開國家的百多年間，內地發生翻天覆地的變化，例如兩次重大政權輪替，近年又有首雙航母下水、開展人類有史以來最大的廉政風暴，強調國家歷史發展不因香港缺席而停滯不前，「香港不在家，但家裡的日子還是要過的」，所以內地不會因香港回歸，而放棄現行良好的司法制度。<br />\n<br />\n同時，王亦指即使強調國家不會因為香港回歸而更改制度，但亦作出重大的法律制度補充，譬如訂立一國兩制、加入釋法制度、特區制度、以及同時沒有按傳統馬克思主義，更換所有公務人員、法官等。最後他寄語港人，要珍惜中華民族經探索得來的憲法制度，以及國家來之不易的安定局面，因即使回歸時有內戰，也是要回歸祖國。"},{"pid":"ff379a5791c90298143e212eb9d83035782b9256","tid":220776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56625268&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56625268%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d27cfb77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56625268%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&h=d7c9eeaf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56625268&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428</a>"},{"pid":"f46a97b07621a0cf4746b40db0b35c8e9b410d8a","tid":220776,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中聯辦法律部部長王振民出席《紫荊》一國兩制論壇致辭時，指由1985至1990年制訂《基本法》、到1997香港回歸時，中國不是一張白紙，不是沒有憲法、沒有制度的國家，而且香港這「遊子」離開國家的百多年間，內地發生翻天覆地的變化，例如兩次重大政權輪替，近年又有首雙航母下水、開展人類有史以來最大的廉政風暴，強調國家歷史發展不因香港缺席而停滯不前，「香港不在家，但家裡的日子還是要過的」，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以內地不會因香港回歸，而放棄現行良好的司法制度。</span><br />\n<br />\n同時，王亦指即使強調國家不會因為香港回歸而更改制度，但亦作出重大的法律制度補充，譬如訂立一國兩制、加入釋法制度、特區制度、以及同時沒有按傳統馬克思主義，更換所有公務人員、法官等。最後他寄語港人，要珍惜中華民族經探索得來的憲法制度，以及國家來之不易的安定局面，因即使回歸時有內戰，也是要回歸祖國。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7831d73e59b533acce6258ae821af08f03545d30","tid":220776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efeb9739817774f1a7f2b8d3ae42717ab924c5d","tid":220776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec333f9727b1afaee582f080bab5024c9d3fa37","tid":220776,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"今日咁多笑話聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9839b62ae5e0f862a4a9b5bc88c74d5fa19c94ee","tid":220776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日咁多笑話聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d4dd3da2cd480cf6c22c3a87f6277a316cc486","tid":220776,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:30:01.000